^Help - Colours
USAGE: .colours
 
This is an enhancement to ^bold^.
 
To use colour, merely type a number immediately following the bold
character.  (The bold character is^ ^^^.)
 
^^1 = ^1BLUE^, ^^2 = ^2GREEN^, ^^3 = ^3RED^, ^^4 = ^4MAGENTA^, ^^5 = ^5CYAN^, ^^6 = ^6YELLOW^,
^^7 = ^7WHITE^, ^^8 = ^8R^8A^8N^8D^8O^8M^.
 
